{
  "text": "Our main …nding is that, somewhat counter-intuitively, the relation between polarization and the stability threshold is ambiguous. Recall [CITATION_1] ), that the concept of polarization is based on the existence of several population clusters with relative homogeneity of preferences within clusters and substantial heterogeneity across clusters.",
  "correct_citation": {
